{
  "file": "937_Kunamalla和Maity - 2023 - Production of green jet fuel from furanics via hydroxyalkylation-alkylation over mesoporous MoO3-ZrO.txt",
  "model": "deepseek-chat",
  "experiment_info": {
    "experiment_count": 2,
    "experiments": [
      {
        "experiment_id": 1,
        "reaction_type": "羟烷基化-烷基化反应",
        "reaction_type_english": "Hydroxyalkylation-alkylation reaction",
        "description": "在介孔MoO3-ZrO2催化剂上，研究2-甲基呋喃与糠醛的羟烷基化-烷基化反应。考察了催化剂煅烧温度、MoO3负载量、反应温度、催化剂用量和反应物摩尔比对2-甲基呋喃转化率的影响。最佳条件为：873 K煅烧温度，20 wt% MoO3负载量，323 K反应温度，1.25 g催化剂，2:1的2-甲基呋喃/糠醛摩尔比，反应5小时，实现了约85%的2-甲基呋喃转化率。",
        "text_snippet": "The HAA reaction of 2-methylfuran with furfural was thus investigated over a novel MoO3-promoted mesoporous ZrO2 catalyst... About 85 % 2-methylfuran conversion was achieved over 1.25 g of this optimum catalyst at 2:1 2-methylfuran/furfural mole ratio, 323 K, and 5 h.",
        "reaction_type_classify": "Hydrogenation reaction"
      },
      {
        "experiment_id": 2,
        "reaction_type": "加氢脱氧反应",
        "reaction_type_english": "Hydrodeoxygenation reaction",
        "description": "在Co/γ-Al2O3催化剂上，研究C15生物燃料前驱体的加氢脱氧反应。考察了反应温度、初始氢压和Co金属负载量对含氧中间体化合物转化率和产物分布的影响。反应路径涉及呋喃环饱和、开环反应，以及加氢脱氧、脱羰和叔碳键断裂的组合。最佳条件为：20 wt% Co负载量，573 K反应温度，30 bar氢压，实现了含氧中间体化合物近乎完全的转化，生成C9-C15烷烃（喷气燃料范围）。",
        "text_snippet": "HDO of biofuel precursor was examined over Co/γ-Al2O3 catalyst at various reaction temperatures, initial hydrogen pressure, and Co metal loading on γ-Al2O3 to understand the reaction mechanism and identify the optimum reaction conditions... Nearly complete conversion of oxygen-containing intermediate compounds to green jet fuel was achieved over 20 wt% Co/γ-Al2O3 at 573 K and 30 bar.",
        "reaction_type_classify": "Hydrogenation reaction"
      }
    ]
  },
